create a attendance web app in which a code is genrated by the the teacher and it has validity timer (10sec-60sec) the student must enter the code before the timeer runs out

structure-
login page
|
|--(Teacher interface)choose class -- genrate code,select timeer,see attendance,mark attendance manually
|
|--(student interface)--enter code,see their attendance
|
|--(admin interface)-- add student,add class,add teacher

